{"tid":1609463,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"入黎睇下被圈養既香港垃圾，再反省下而家打唔打恐怖份子","createTime":"2019-10-01T14:38:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T15:56:41.000Z","uid":34241,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"57b89dc25313af453a246178a9a5aa53da9d72cc","tid":1609463,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:38:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>警拍攝餐廳內市民容貌  指罵市民「垃圾」<br />\n明報即時新聞FB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=925756647823055\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D925756647823055&d=JxnAwUrH%2B1qYxVTFfur%2BVq9osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=08d8c824\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=925756647823055</a><br />\n後備: <a href=\"https://streamable.com/b6w14\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fb6w14&d=JxnAwUrH%2B1qYxVTFfur%2BVq9osQ3F9Lpm1EhhEwxE9Bk%3D&h=36372787\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/b6w14</a></blockquote><br />\n１隻full gear，蒙面：「不知所謂，垃圾！擰返個頭出黎呀！」<br />\n另１隻手持ｃａｍ影向室內：「做咩擰轉頭呀？擰返個頭出黎丫！」（有人拍打玻璃）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>香港人，你睇下你係幾咁廢柴,幾咁懦弱</strong></span></span><br />\n一班<span style=\"color: red;\">由香港人比錢養住</span>既恐怖份子已經如此囂張跋扈<br />\n對住餐廳內既平民都如斯恐嚇<br />\n幾十個防暴，１支ＣＡＭ，已經嚇到成班人瀨哂屎<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>香港人仲要忍到幾時？？仲可以等到幾時？？</strong></span></span><br />\n香港人已經比呢班恐怖份子踩左落地獄<br />\n冇得翻轉頭架喇！唔好再叫解散警隊、追究責任喇！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不與恐怖份子談判、傾畢生之力殲滅恐怖份子！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n由今晚開始，全香港（包括內外文宣）都要改口叫<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>「殲滅恐怖份子！<br />\n擊潰恐怖組織！<br />\n鏟除極權政府！」</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">唔好以為你安坐家中、隔住個ｍｏｎ食花生，咩都唔關你事<br />\n唔好以為你著住街坊ＬＯＯＫ，周圍食花生唔主動進犯就唔會打你<br />\n唔好以為你中立、唔參與抗爭，班恐怖份子就唔會搞你</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>你班港豬係狗黎咋！<br />\n你班港豬係垃圾黎咋！<br />\n香港幾撚時輪到你話事！<br />\n同我跪低含柒啦！曱甴！<br />\n你只係一隻被圈養既賤種港豬黎咋！<br />\n曱甴都學人搞革命？收皮啦！<br />\n</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我要呢條片傳遍全香港每一部手機<br />\n每一個ＦＢ、ＩＧ、ＴＷＩＴＴＥＲ　ＡＣ<br />\n越王勾踐臥薪嘗膽<br />\n香港人自己每日重溫！<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>記住今日既恥辱！<br />\n昨日仇，今日報！<br />\n不報此仇，誓不為人！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>殲滅恐怖份子，人人有責！<br />\n擊潰恐怖組織，當仁不讓！<br />\n香港再無警察，只有恐怖份子！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>咪撚再講對準政權<br />\n極權政府所支持既極端激進恐怖組織已經將香港人推入死路！<br />\n唔殲滅恐怖份子只有死路一條！</strong></span>"},{"pid":"4434b6d2a36ee00238c698cdff630b15ad046869","tid":1609463,"uid":119609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:38:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MwX28K1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMwX28K1.png&h=3d12936a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f38bb4a06ae745f61a1eff619767c1fb4528f51","tid":1609463,"uid":322508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:39:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ztsyv9i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fztsyv9i.jpg&h=7771cca0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/drCFVAZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdrCFVAZ.jpg&h=da62c5cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"27979535294c3b3613ba16f1cbf9137163e72356","tid":1609463,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:42:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>自己香港自己救！<br />\n文宣武鬥同攜手！<br />\n<br />\n全民皆兵！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">（打完覺得好老土）<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"736359f6729a854aeb74df6eca2fdb3ca4d0e7f2","tid":1609463,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:48:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>班恐怖份子當打仗咁打<br />\n當你曱甴咁捽死<br />\n你仲忍得到？！<br />\n仲要和理非？！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"95fec74fa17a5f535f082f70cc574cdfa78cc898","tid":1609463,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:52:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea1ff4bc291db503ddf009b214958939775224aa","tid":1609463,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:56:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}